name: Kessil A150W LEDs + Gooseneck + Free $35 credit

Receive $35 in LIVESTOCK CREDIT with the purchase of any Kessil and Gooseneck Combo!


YOUR COLOR CHOICES

* A150W SKY BLUE: 10000K Special Blend The Sky Blues distinctive spectrum emits light similar to a 10000K light. Bask your corals in a natural-looking light that shines optimum wavelengths for growth.
* A150W OCEAN BLUE: 15000K Special Blend The Ocean Blue model delivers a unique mix of wavelengths that resemble a 15000K light. Create a visually stunning shimmer effect in your reef tank while your corals grow to new heights.
* A150W DEEP OCEAN BLUE: 20000K Special Blend Choose Deep Ocean Blue to produce a deep blue hue in your underwater world. The special blend of wavelengths emulates a 20000K light and creates a truly lifelike environment for your wet pets.
* A150W AMAZON SUN: 6700K Special Blend brings the power of the sun to your freshwater tank. This model is a true 6,700 K light that promotes lush plants and vibrant aquascapes.
